dc_description_s: This point data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Iron County, Wisconsin in 2018.[Classify by [type] field...Survey = Survey-grade coordinatesLandnet = WI State Landnet coordinatesGPS = Recreational-grade coordinatesGPS+ = Might be better than recreational-grade coordinatesGIS = Calculated location from other corners and surveys.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
